Localization.Name: Testudo Backpack Disrupt Camo
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Backpack
Carrying Capacity: 105K µSCU
Core Compatibility: Medium & Heavy

The Testudo backpack may feel as light as a feather in your hands, but it can hold an impressive amount of weight thanks to its use of the same tough yet lightweight plating as the armor set.

The Disrupt Camo edition utilizes carbon fiber grays and blacks printed in a disruptive pattern to keep your enemies guessing.
